Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Brotherhood
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 29
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,===============================================================

Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:43.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where the hell are you taking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:44.40,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:04.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:07.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Military Headquarters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.51,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.32,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:21.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have dreamed the Homunculi's hideout was under Headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:26.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So it means that the army is also associated with them, not just the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:31.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But I've got something good to tell you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:37.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! You really found my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:39.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:43.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Although you told me,\N"You're not my soul, so I can't come with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Great, so my body still exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:55.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This just means we're one step closer to our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:00.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why do you still have that cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:01.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, inside of me, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That midget?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Stop being so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and put your underwear on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:13.04,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.00,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:28.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, why the hell did you have to bring her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:31.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There was no other choice. She's injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:31.78,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.98,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the rest to Wrath. Go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President King Bradley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:55.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:04:01.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Fuery was transferred to the South, Warrant Officer Falman to the North,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,and Second Lieutenant Breda to the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:06.73,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,And Lieutenant Hawkeye is going to be an assistant to the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's no more than taking hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.36,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:25.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's just us and the Führer President in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And he only has one weapon; a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:31.83,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, he's still confident he can beat all three of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:44.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You came to visit me in the hospital once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:51.30,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't meddle in things.\NThink of the entire army as your enemy."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:53.61,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.78,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You are all important to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.48,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to know about the minor details,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:03.92,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,but behave until the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:06.86,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you keep that promise, we won't harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:12.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And when that time comes, what'll happen to the civilians who aren't "human sacrifices" like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:16.70,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you. You don't need to know the minor details,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.50,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"Fullmetal Alchemist", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:27.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I chose to become a dog of the military in order to get my body back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:34.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But the State Alchemist Institution itself was probably created to pick out these sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:38.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to be used by you guys again on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:43.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I quit my job as a State Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:48.20,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Your proof of being a dog is covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:53.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you guys are planning, I'll put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell the other alchemists, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.71,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What was her name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.88,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Winry Rockbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.29,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Born in Resembool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:09.30,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,A childhood friend of yours\Nand someone who is practically family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.64,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,A skilled automail mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:16.47,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,She currently works at Rush Valley,\Nand she's loved by her customers and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.54,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good, obedient girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lay a finger on her and see what happens! People around her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.36,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:32.07,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,If you still want to quit, then I'll cut her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.07,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.09,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:45.83,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We get the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:54.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Like before, please let us continue to search for clues\Nfor getting our bodies back while being under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:55.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:58.39,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.98,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't interfere with our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.01,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Colonel Mustang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:06.11,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to tell me that you plan to resign from the military too, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:11.78,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... even if I became a dog of the military, I'd rather not become a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:20.29,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, because of my ambition, I won't be able to take off this uniform or get rid of this. For now, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.67,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.29,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You all may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:30.22,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you one thing, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.57,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.64,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who killed Hughes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.18,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.43,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Then who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:42.94,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You said "one thing", did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.90,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.41,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Wait a moment, Alphonse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... Is there something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:05.68,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,No, you may leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.80,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,A sword just went right over my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:17.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Money. Lend me some change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.35,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:23.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:28.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:29.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:30.90,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.49,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.82,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We'll report everything later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.52,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.09,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, the Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:47.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieute-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.98,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:53.84,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:59.96,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Can you blame me for feeling sick after seeing a musclehead when I was expecting to see a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.21,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.10,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.38,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:06.09,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:09.36,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Hawkeye, just returning from the restroom, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:14.12,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I accepted Major Armstrong's kindness and had him take my place for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.92,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.37,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:24.62,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one who told me\Nto never give up no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:30.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't regret later that you didn't run away, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.37,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Like I will after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:37.82,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.98,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed? What's with the sudden call?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.04,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Did you break your automail again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Anything new in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:51.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're not being stalked by anyone, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.32,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:54.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.82,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You're being creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:05.01,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's rare enough for you to call, and it turns out you're worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:08.08,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, there's something wrong here.\NI bet it's going to snow tonight or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Do you have any idea how much I-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:10.96,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.65,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy you called.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.72,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:20.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So you're really okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:23.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:28.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Good, she was fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:31.47,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,It's your excitable nature that lets people take advantage of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:35.65,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.01,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Your buddy asked me to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:41.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ling did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:44.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is in Xing's language, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.41,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.16,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He wants you to give it to the woman waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:52.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fa-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:56.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're not planning on following us and killing her, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:58.22,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that low.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.55,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't like fighting girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:05.43,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.77,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Later. Be sure to give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.59,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.13,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:35.29,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What reason did he have to start the civil war\Nwhen it would ruin this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.45,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.26,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.85,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,You're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.88,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Could you come down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.38,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to know what's going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.60,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine; the guard won't be coming again for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:01.74,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a doctor. I'll tend your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.30,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,An Ishbalan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.78,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,That scar on your forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.21,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... You're Scar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.28,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.96,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.22,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:28.47,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:32.98,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also an alchemist who assisted in the Ishbal Extermination!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:40.36,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine. Nothing life-threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:43.10,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,She'll get better as long as she gets some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.95,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank goodness" my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.49,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Giving me more patients by the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.23,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Both my bed and sofa are occupied!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:53.00,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell am I supposed to sleep, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.20,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.89,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, two patients in my house at once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.73,Default-alt,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:57.89,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:00.32,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:03.49,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Is... Is the young master not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine. He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.18,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:17.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:24.07,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,He says... He says he's obtained a philosopher's stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.63,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,With this, our clan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:32.95,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I must return to my country immediately and tell my people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.68,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where is the young master?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:39.88,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why won't you speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.25,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me something happened to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.15,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:45.55,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the young master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.99,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,How is your body feeling, Greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.91,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.23,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:14:00.31,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear? This body belongs to a prince of Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:05.78,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted power that would help him become Emperor, and thus accepted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.46,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He's a really interesting guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:14.09,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Him and I once had a discussion on what it means to be a true king.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:20.09,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,He said something like, "A King exists for his people. Without his people, there is no King."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:25.18,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot. He gave in to greed and lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:26.73,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.97,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:32.37,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:37.18,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He's vigilantly watching for a chance to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:41.56,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,He's even planning on taking control of a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.16,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,How greedy can these humans get?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:53.03,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President is a Homunculus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:15:01.05,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been my honor to fight for the weak citizens of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:06.62,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Many people feel the same,\Nbelieve in the military, and sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:10.07,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, the military itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.48,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Why not resign?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,With your personality, being a soldier will only hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.44,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! This is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:26.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going against military command?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:29.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! Call for a replacement State Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:36.42,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I ran from battle during Ishbal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.60,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,...because I thought what the army was doing was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:45.17,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,But instead, I should have fought against it instead of running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:53.44,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, not a day has passed that I didn't feel ashamed for bending my principles and fleeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:16:01.85,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,And this time, if the army itself is the battlefield, how can I run away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:07.40,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:11.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I told the Führer President I wouldn't quit because I still have an ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:19.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The fact the Führer President revealed he's a Homunculus means that even if he was to be defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:22.29,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,there's still someone else in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:24.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.46,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's an honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.96,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,You're being pretty calm about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.21,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:35.47,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same when I fought that other Homunculus, Lust, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:41.39,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Although people accuse me of being a "weapon" and a "monster", when fighting against real monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:45.35,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...I truly feel as though I'm nothing but an ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:48.90,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.90,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,So the young master took in the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:54.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:56.95,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had been able to stop him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.02,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.93,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,I am only mad at myself for not being able to fulfill my duty as a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.42,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:10.01,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,So the young master is still inside this Greed person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:16.92,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse, I want a replacement arm. And quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:19.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But... it'll take some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:22.52,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Please introduce me to an automail mechanic! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I will soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to get better before I do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:38.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get you something to eat from Dr. Nox...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.76,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You can get up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:43.04,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... was your name May Chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.04,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,May?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:49.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.13,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of the Yao Clan's watchdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:56.26,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,And you're... the Chan Clan's successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.38,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.05,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the 17th Princess of Xing, May Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:59.61,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.68,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here in this country, it means... you're after immortality, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.44,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you and your clan have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.73,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even be able to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:16.47,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but let's play nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:19.41,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere with our country's affairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:19.41,Default-alt,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere with our country's affairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.16,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me just because I'm injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:25.16,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.25,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.88,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Patients should be asleep in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.13,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere with our country's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:39.51,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I care about your country's affairs, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.30,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:44.10,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Patients are patients, no matter what country they're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.63,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning on messing up my house even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.71,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:54.98,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard about cases where unknown pathogens mysteriously appear in a doctor's house and kill everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.53,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,...right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,This place really is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:05.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he have anyone to clean for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.58,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:14.71,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:18.85,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Isn't this a picture of your family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.18,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,It's my divorced wife and my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:23.06,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:26.16,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I'm free to do whatever I want with my stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.59,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Have a cup of coffee after this is all cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:38.15,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:41.00,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:43.37,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I was at a loss about what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:51.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Now that I think about it, I can use alchemy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:20:01.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice work! This is all for the repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.29,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, State Alchemists are something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:06.83,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,On a totally different level from other alchemists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:12.53,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, we asked nearby alchemists to help us this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:14.97,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,They were completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:20.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They came to the scene all full of themselves, and as soon as they were getting started, they told us it wasn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:22.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,In the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:24.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's around the time we were underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.39,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.58,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:41.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really believe what Envy said?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:47.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That those people are only made of energy, without a body or a soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:52.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together! Think about the future, not the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:21:00.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But at that time, other alchemists aside from Al and I were unable to use alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:04.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But that midget and Scar could.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy that's different from ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:15.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I could find out the secret behind it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:22.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,there may be a way to get Al's body back and fight against that geezer without using a philosopher's stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.89,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I have to return this to the Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscy70}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscy70}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscy70}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:11.11,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,They made me help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.74,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I created philosopher's stones and took the lives of many Ishbalans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:23.65,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I'm on the verge of being forced to work on an experiment that would cause more deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:25.13,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.37,0:23:28.02,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,So please, I'm begging you! Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:29.38,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:32.64,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get back at them with death!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:40.35,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, in my eyes, you appear as God...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.62,0:23:48.02,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't told me everything about Ishbal yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:49.94,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you bastards do there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:52.57,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me everything, Marcoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:55.63,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Before my right hand destroys you!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:24:01.29,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Force. Never-ending violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:03.87,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The earth is drowned in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:06.88,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The air is choked with the stench of burnt flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:09.05,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Ishbal...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:11.76,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A detestable memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.96,0:24:17.22,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:20.85,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 30, Ishbal Extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.86,0:24:23.53,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,I will recite the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.53,0:24:25.56,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.56,0:24:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
